":"영국 에세스 숍랜드","lifeSummary":"Henry de Tibetot(은)는 대략 1200년 영국 노르스벌랜드 버윅-업-트위드에서 Walter de Tibetot의 아들로 태어났다. 그는 1228년 이전 영국에서 Alda de Nettlestead(와)과 결혼했다. 그들은 적어도 두 명의 아들을 두었다. 그는 1250년 5월 22일 영국 요르크실르 후턴 파그넬에서 51세의 나이로 사망했으며 영국 에세스에 묻혔다."},"lv":{"about 1200–22 May 1250":"ap 1200. gadu–1250. gada 22. maijs","1200–1250":"1200–1250","1210–1241":"1210–1241","1228–1298":"1228.gads–1298","1228–1270":"1228.gads–1270","1180–Male":"1180–miris","after 22 May 1250":"pēc 1250. gada 22. maija","December 1241":"1241. gada decembris","1241":"1241","22 May 1250":"1250. gada 22. maijs","1250":"1250","1270":"1270","before 1228":"pirms 1228. gada","1180":"1180","1228":"1228. gads","1215":"1215","after 1228":"pēc 1228. gada","1224":"1224","1200":"1200","1298":"1298","1210":"1210","about 1200":"ap 1200. gadu","Hooton Pagnell, Yorkshire, England":"Hooton Pagnell, Yorkshire, England","Berwick-upon-Tweed, Northumberland, England":"Berwick-upon-Tweed, Northumberland, England","England":"England","Wymondham, Leicestershire, England":"Wymondham, Leicestershire, England","Essex, England":"Essex, England","Shopland, Essex, England":"Shopland, Essex, England"},"mg":{"about 1200–22 May 1250":"tany ho any amin'ny 1200–22 mey 1250","1200–1250":"1200–1250","1210–1241":"1210–1241","1228–1298":"1228–1298","1228–1270":"1228–1270","1180–Male":"1180–Maty","after 22 May 1250":"taorian'ny 22 mey 1250","December 1241":"desambra 1241","1241":"1241","22 May 1250":"22 mey 1250","1250":"1250","1270":"1270","before 1228":"talohan'ny 1228","1180":"1180","1228":"1228","1215":"1215","after 1228":"taorian'ny 1228","1224":"1224","1200":"1200","1298":"1298","1210":"1210","about 1200":"tany ho any amin'ny 1200","Hooton Pagnell, Yorkshire, England":"Hooton Pagnell, Yorkshire, England","Berwick-upon-Tweed, Northumberland, England":"Berwick-upon-Tweed, Northumberland, England","England":"England","Wymondham, Leicestershire, England":"Wymondham, Leicestershire, England","Essex, England":"Essex, England","Shopland, Essex